article_title: Sam Youngman: Does Alison Lundergan Grimes have time to tell voters who she is?
article_text: Democratic U.S. Senate candidate Alison Lundergan Grimes' latest ad is a continuation of what has become a central theme of her campaign: Telling voters who she isn't instead of telling them who she is.
